reviewText: Sounds like someone recorded this with a cell phone. Horrible quality.

Keith is not just a crooner or strutter like some male singers.  He can write songs, play a mean guitar, and perform with the best of them.  He's a triple threat!  He's a musician's musician!  He is one of the best country musicians ever.

Its Keith Urban, so its hard to screw something up, but they managed to make a pretty poor "documentary." This video is basically a few really old clips that nobody wants to watch. Video quality is poor at best. What music is on there is someone recording with a hand recorder from decades ago. Poor positioning, ect. The "Keith Urban: Love pain and the whole crazy world tour" DVD blows this out of the water. Not to mention it comes with two for less than the price of this.
